sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor Dev as Developer
    participant AppRepo as App Repository (GitHub)
    participant CI as GitHub Actions CI Runner
    participant GHCR as GHCR OCI Registry
    participant NuGet as GitHub Packages NuGet Feed
    participant GitOps as GitHub Actions CD Runner
    participant PolicyTools as Policy Tools
    participant OCP as OpenShift Cluster

    rect rgb(220, 235, 255)
        Note over Dev,GHCR: CI — Build, Test, Package
        Dev->>AppRepo: git push (PR or merge to main)
        AppRepo->>CI: Trigger CI workflow
        CI->>CI: dotnet restore (dotnet-8-dependencies.yml)
        CI->>CI: dotnet build --configuration Release (dotnet-8-build.yml)
        CI->>CI: dotnet test + coverage enforcement (dotnet-8-tests-msbuild.yml)
        CI->>CI: dotnet format --verify-no-changes (dotnet-8-lint.yml)
        CI->>GHCR: Push container image (tagged or digest-pinned)
        CI-->>AppRepo: Upload test-results artifact (7 days)
        opt NuGet library
            CI->>CI: dotnet pack to .nupkg (dotnet-8-nuget-pack.yml)
            CI->>NuGet: dotnet nuget push (dotnet-8-nuget-deploy.yml)
        end
    end

    rect rgb(220, 255, 230)
        Note over Dev,OCP: CD — Render, Validate, Deploy
        Dev->>AppRepo: Merge to main / create release tag
        AppRepo->>GitOps: Trigger CD workflow
        GitOps->>GHCR: helm registry login
        GitOps->>GHCR: helm dependency update — pulls ag-helm-templates OCI chart
        GHCR-->>GitOps: ag-helm-templates.tgz
        GitOps->>GitOps: helm template my-release ./my-chart — renders to rendered.yaml
        GitOps->>PolicyTools: datree test rendered.yaml (DataClass, AVI annotation, probes, resources)
        PolicyTools-->>GitOps: pass / fail
        GitOps->>PolicyTools: polaris audit rendered.yaml (securityContext, NetworkPolicy, replicas)
        PolicyTools-->>GitOps: pass / fail
        GitOps->>PolicyTools: kube-linter lint rendered.yaml (selectors, RBAC, image tags)
        PolicyTools-->>GitOps: pass / fail
        GitOps->>PolicyTools: conftest test rendered.yaml (OPA Rego — allow-all NP, edge termination, internet egress)
        PolicyTools-->>GitOps: pass / fail
        GitOps->>OCP: helm upgrade --install my-release ./my-chart
        OCP-->>GitOps: release deployed
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 220)
        Note over OCP: Runtime — OpenShift cluster
        OCP->>OCP: Apply Deployment / StatefulSet / Job
        OCP->>OCP: Apply Service (ClusterIP only — enforced by policy)
        OCP->>OCP: Apply OpenShift Route + AVI infrasetting annotation
        OCP->>OCP: Apply NetworkPolicy (deny-by-default, only explicit allows pass)
        OCP->>OCP: Apply HPA / PDB / PriorityClass
        OCP-->>Dev: Application reachable at Route host
    end